snippet.title: Game & Watch - Boxing (Micro Vs. System) (c)1984 Nintendo [MAME emulation footage]
snippet.description:
This is Boxing, part of Nintendo's Micro Vs. System series, which is closely related to the Game & Watch series.  This was released in some territories as Punch Out, although it is 100% identical apart from the title printed on the unit.  This was first emulated back in MAME 0.194, before many of the other Game and Watch units were emulated.  This video reflects the state of it in 2020 with current artwork files.

Game & Watch artwork for MAME was done by DarthMarino (more recently emulated units) and hydef (units emulated before 2020)
